<div class="topic-card"><strong>Introduction</strong></div>

<section class="chapter-section">
<div class="chapter-text">
<p><span style="font-size:18px;">Hey kids! Congratulations on reaching the end of the course. For your capstone project, you&#39;ll get to be a real designer and create a fun website or landing page for Salty Jewellery using Gamma (<a href="https://gamma.app">gamma.app</a>). Gamma is like a magic AI tool that helps you build beautiful pages super easily&mdash;no coding needed!</span></p>

<p><br />
<span style="font-size:18px;">You can choose:</span></p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Option 1:</strong> Make your own jewellery website, showing off imaginary or real pieces you design (like bracelets, necklaces, or earrings inspired by the sea).</li>
	<li><strong>Option 2:</strong> Create a landing page for Salty Jewellery, highlighting their cool collections, materials, and why they&#39;re awesome.</li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:18px;">This project is all about creativity, so add pictures, colors, and fun facts from what you&#39;ve learned in the course. Once done, you&#39;ll share the link in a simple document and submit it to your LMS (like Google Classroom or whatever your school uses). Let&#39;s make it sparkle!</span></p>
</div>
