<div class="topic-card"><strong>Part 1: Creating Your Project in Gamma</strong></div>

<section class="chapter-section">
<div class="chapter-text">
<p><span style="font-size:18px;">Gamma makes this fun and fast. Follow these steps to build your page. It should take about 30-60 minutes!</span></p>

<h2><strong>Step 1: Sign Up and Start for Free</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Go to <a href="https://gamma.app">gamma.app</a> on your computer or tablet.</li>
	<li>Click &quot;Start for free&quot; and make an account (ask a grown-up if you need help&mdash;it&rsquo;s quick and free!).</li>
	<li>Once logged in, click &quot;Create new&quot; to start a new project. Choose &quot;Webpage&quot; or &quot;Landing page&quot; mode.</li>
</ul>

<h2><strong>Step 2: Plan Your Idea</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Think about what to include! For Salty Jewellery, add sections like:</li>
	<li>A welcome title: &quot;Welcome to Salty Jewellery &ndash; Sparkly Treasures from the Sea!&quot;</li>
	<li>Pictures of jewellery (upload your drawings or use free images from the course).</li>
	<li>Fun facts: &quot;Made with brass alloy for durability!&quot; or &quot;Anti-tarnish so it shines forever!&quot;</li>
	<li>A call to action: &quot;Buy now or design your own!&quot;</li>
	<li>Type a simple prompt like: &quot;Create a landing page for Salty Jewellery with sections for designs, materials, and contact.&quot; Gamma&rsquo;s AI will generate a starting page for you!</li>
</ul>

<h2><strong>Step 3: Add Content with AI Help</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Gamma will create a basic page&mdash;now customize it!</li>
	<li>Add text: Click on a section and type about the jewellery. Use AI by clicking &quot;Generate&quot; to make it fancier, like &quot;Make this description more exciting for kids!&quot;</li>
	<li>Add images: Upload photos of jewellery or use AI to generate ones (type &quot;Generate image of a shiny necklace with crystals&quot;). Make it colorful with blues and sparkles for that salty vibe.</li>
	<li>Add sections: Use the + button to include lists of materials (like enamel for color) or benefits (from the course, e.g., &quot;Skin-friendly and affordable!&quot;).</li>
</ul>

<h2><strong>Step 4: Customize and Make It Pretty</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Choose a theme: Pick a fun, bright one from Gamma&rsquo;s 100+ options&mdash;maybe something ocean-themed with waves or gems.</li>
	<li>Edit layouts: Drag and drop sections to rearrange. Add buttons like &quot;Learn More&quot; or sliders to show multiple jewellery pieces.</li>
	<li>Preview: Click &quot;Preview&quot; to see how it looks on a phone or computer. Make sure it&rsquo;s easy to read and super sparkly!</li>
</ul>

<h2><strong>Step 5: Share Your Creation</strong></h2>

<ul>
	<li>Click &quot;Publish&quot; or &quot;Share&quot; to get a link to your page.</li>
	<li>Copy the URL&mdash;that&rsquo;s your website link! Test it by opening in a new tab to make sure it works.</li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:18px;">Your page is now live! Show it to your family for feedback.</span></p>
</div>
